<h3>Expense Tracker notification - Weekly digest</h3>

This is the weekly report for all expense lists with notifications enabled.

<% expense_lists_with_notifications_enabled.each do |expense_list| %>
<h4><%= expense_list.name %></h4>
<p>Expenses in <%= current_month_name.downcase %> so far: <i><%= expense_list.sum_of_exp_in_month(current_month, current_year) %>€</i></p>
<p>Money left in <%= current_month_name.downcase %>: <i><%= expense_list.euros_left_in_month(current_month, current_year) %>€</i></p>
<p><i>Forgot to submit any expenses this week? <%= link_to 'Click here', new_expense_list_expense_url(expense_list) %> to add what you've spent!</i></p>
<% end %>

<p>
  Greetings,
  your expense tracker
</p>
